Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:04.67,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, there was a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:10.70,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect his friend, the\Nwarrior took his friend's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.01,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, there was a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:19.58,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword had continued to fight for the sake of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:24.62,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,It realized that in order to protect the peace, it had no\Nchoice but to kill the one who wielded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.65,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus it took its master's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:35.09,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The warrior and the sword had no choice but to do as they\Ndid, but was that really what they ought to have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:39.63,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncertain of the answer even now,\Nthey wander aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere else left to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:14.51,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Warrior's Fountain"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Tutu isn't around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...helped me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,tried to restore a piece of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Kraehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraehe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:46.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Kraehe, dressed like a black bird\Ntook my heart shard and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Fakir, don't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I need to regain my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:05.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me. I brought you back here, because I\Nthought it would be safer with people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your worries to rest and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:41.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Mytho's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What do you mean that I brought you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know a lot of things, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:53.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, because\NI'm the desire for knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire for knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember how you brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I did? You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you don black feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:04.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a special power dwelling within you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, tell me, which is the real you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.63,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I most certainly saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Confessing your love at the window?! Ahiru, you're so bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a reverse Romeo and Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:49.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it's horribly different since it's one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I was doing. Mytho's disappeared and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I forgot about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't been to class in a long time now, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you couldn't contain yourself\Nand resolved to confess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this chance to attack, attack, attack all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.83,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, you have no hope, since Mytho-sama has Rue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it and take your losses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose and be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He might show up to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeful, aren't you? You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mytho will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does, you have to say it properly and clearly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, what else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:29.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That you love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't say that to him! Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I said that, I'd disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked all over town, but I couldn't find you, so\NI was wondering what had happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so relieved to see you were okay and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:21.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, he doesn't know that I'm Tutu, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:26.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:43.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, you go ahead. I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully. Never come near Mytho again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:04.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go near him again, I'll make sure you pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:19.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So what happened in the end? Did she fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:22.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She got turned down in a somewhat\Nsubdued manner, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to get her to do a revenge match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Tutu return a piece of Mytho's heart to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho also wished for its return...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I saw that, and after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up skipping the morning classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:56.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The look in Fakir's eyes that time was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho shouldn't be with someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Edel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:14.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Edel-san, I want to save Mytho from Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fakir told me not to go near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:20.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So... or rather... but, but um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this gem is "Courage."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a single gem made of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A single gem made of two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:33.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that I should work together with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But with whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't put Rue-chan in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Restore my heart to me, Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:48.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If I let Mytho know that I'm Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:52.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, together, we might be able to stand up... to Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he to you, Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not really anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:03.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a dangerous person to Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Edel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua... Quack, quack, quack, quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:29.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it! It's Mytho's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack, quack, quack, quack, quack, quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,An iguana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you're going to find food in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you wouldn't have wandered in if you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:23.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua... Quack, quack, quack, quack, quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:25.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack, quack, quack. Quack. Quack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:25.44,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:29.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on home. Don't come around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it was like he wasn't the usual Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go near him again, I'll make sure you pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Of course, he's definitely a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be fooled just because the bread was tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably acted like that only because I was just a duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:54.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to tell Mytho everything, I better tell him\Nthat I'm just a duck too, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru says she has something important to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be waiting in the school's backyard at\N5 o'clock this evening, Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the girl not hear what I said to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can throw it away. There's no need for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:36.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What would be the point in seeing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:41.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She might know something about Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:41.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, there's no way she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:45.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her existence will only bring you\Nunhappiness. Don't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, there's that Kraehe coming after you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you no, it's no! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I can no longer stop Mytho with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the prince's own sword, which\Nonce shattered his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what do you plan to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:25.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword shattered the prince's heart\Nand destroyed the evil raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, grant it power once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, er... Oh, er, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:18.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I... uh, actually... actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way! You knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Tutu, don't you, Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you scared me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir told me that I shouldn't come here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You talked to Fakir about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:40.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everything I tell Mytho goes straight to Fakir too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:41.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:50.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think of Tutu, I become filled\Nwith the desire to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with Tutu always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My prince, you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:32.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of a treasure is most clearly\Nrevealed when it is fought over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:38.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who will the prince go to, Princess Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:59.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair, your cheeks, and even your heart all belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Kraehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return the piece of his heart that you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop making the prince suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:08.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:16.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, my prince, there is the one\Nmaking you suffer. Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:19.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No... She's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My poor prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:25.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you need is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:29.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:30.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are like a doll, but I will love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you forget about Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall just give this heart thing to the crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the prince's sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're Kraehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not address me so familiarly, you filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a manifestation of the raven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry you had to wait so long, Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:29.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right now. You won't have to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:30.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:36.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shatter your heart for you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.54,0:18:37.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:40.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use now, Princess Tutu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU shattered Mytho's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a terrible thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:54.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This would never have happened if you hadn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:20.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I pierce my heart with this sword,\Nwill that satisfy you, Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Then, you'll return to your old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:26.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd rather be without a heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to her! Quickly, just pierce your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:44.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:45.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, you smiled just a little, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, I thought that must be the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:59.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think if your heart is full, you'll show even more of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's the real you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:25.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save you from the suffering, because all\NI can do is restore your heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:33.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that is the answer you've chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu, restore my heart shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what you think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really only a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:42.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the prince sees is Princess\NTutu in her beautiful dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Was what the sword pierced the prince's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:50.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or someone's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Rue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rue, maybe I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, Princess Tutu will change Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:40.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraehe, why are you in such pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:42.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone, you ugly crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:44.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I am a crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:48.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am the TRUE prima donna, Princess Kraehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:51.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All you children who love stories, come gather around.
